  "synopsis": "The official website for the Tiger &amp; Bunny anime announced on Friday that the Pacifico Yokohama's National Convention Hall of Yokohama would host special Tiger &amp; Bunny concerts September 19th and 20th. The franchise's composer Yoshihiro Ike is personally conducting the \"Sternbild Orchestra &amp; Band\" for live performances of music from the television series and two films.\n\n\"Tiger &amp; Bunny: Too Many Cooks Spoil the Broth\" is an 18 minute episode that was released with the BD of the concert, \"The Sound of Tiger &amp; Bunny\". It features the Heroes of the series being assigned to form a band to play a single performance.\n\n(Source: ANN, edited)",
